		<hr size="1">Gtheb, that post was fine.  Spelling and Grammar problems only matter if it makes your post unintelligible.  The only thing I would do, would be to hit your enter key again, everytime you hit it once.  It will add a blank line between paragraphs making it much easier to read. <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/smile.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle></P><P>As for you question...well, you're not swarm kiting.  You can't really swarm kite w/o charm, which you don't have yet.  You might be aggro kiting, but I don't know for sure.  I barely remember my youth, as it was done before Luclin even existed.  Lastly, I'm not a person to ask about PvP advice.  I don't have much, if any, experience at it.  I can say that your resist songs will play a high priorty against any caster.  Most people, if they have the spell, will immediately try to root/snare a bard because a bard's strong point is being able to move so fast (with Selo's lvl 5 song).<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
